JQuery-Github is a simple script that allows easy access to your github information for a 
website.

Simple usage :

In haml, this is all that is needed to list your repos. 

%h2= "Github Repos"
%ul.githubportal
  :javascript
    $('ul.githubportal').gitHubPortal();
    var gitHubPortal = $('ul.githubportal').data('gitHubPortal');
    gitHubPortal.getRepos("wlaurance")